37260>>>>>    
37260>>>>>    //
37260>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37260>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37260>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37260>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37260>>>>>    //
37260>>>>>    // Params:
37260>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37260>>>>>    //
37260>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37262>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37262>>>>>        
37262>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37263>>>>>        
37263>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37263>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37265>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37266>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37267>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37268>>>>>            
37268>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37269>>>>>        End
37269>>>>>>
37269>>>>>        Else Begin
37270>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37271>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37272>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37273>>>>>            
37273>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37274>>>>>        End
37274>>>>>>
37274>>>>>    End_Procedure
37275>>>>>    
37275>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37277>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37277>>>>>    End_Procedure
37278>>>>>    
37278>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37280>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37280>>>>>    End_Procedure
