37438>>>    // Add a DDO Structure 
37438>>>    //
37438>>>    // There is no need to synchronize a DD structure on the client so we do
37438>>>    // not set the Server property or send ADDOStructure. We will simply use
37438>>>    // DDO's to mine data and generate HTML for our cWebHTMLBox objects.
37438>>>    // It is the HTML in these objects that is sent to the client each time 
37438>>>    // this page is shown.
37438>>>    //
37438>>>    // Also, it is important for the drill-down Navigation interface that we
37438>>>    // do not set the Server property to some DDO because this will affect 
37438>>>    // constraints in the next view that we navigate to.
