38597>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
38600>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38600>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38600>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38600>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38600>>>>>
38600>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38601>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38602>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38603>>>>>
38603>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38603>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38604>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38605>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
38606>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
38607>>>>>
38607>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
38609>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
38610>>>>>        End
38610>>>>>>
38610>>>>>        Else Begin
38611>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38612>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38613>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38614>>>>>        End
38614>>>>>>
38614>>>>>    End_Procedure
